OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778418667
OL,3,CDaniel Dubois defeats Fabio Wardley to
OL,4,Cbecome WBO heavyweight champion
OL,6,FDaniel Dubois is now a two-time
OL,7,Fheavyweight world champion.
OL,9,FThe 28 year old from Greenwich
OL,10,Fsurvived two knockdowns, the first
OL,11,Fafter just 10 seconds, to beat Fabio
OL,12,FWardley in the 11th round of a
OL,13,Fthrilling fight in Manchester. Dubois
OL,14,Fnow holds the WBO version of the
OL,15,Fheavyweight title.
OL,17,FThe professional boxer weathered the
OL,18,Fearly onslaught and started to land
OL,19,Fsome punishing shots of his own,
OL,20,Fleaving Wardley's face bloodied and
OL,21,Fbattered.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
