OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778418667
OL,3,CDaniel Dubois defeats Fabio Wardley to
OL,4,Cbecome WBO heavyweight champion
OL,6,FThe referee ended the match at the
OL,7,Fstart of the penultimate round.
OL,9,FDubois claims he called on his
OL,10,F"warrior spirit" in the ring. He said:
OL,12,F"I had to get back up, bounce it off
OL,13,Fand come back harder. I'm a warrior.
OL,15,F"I had to pull it out the bag and rely
OL,16,Fon (the jab) and use all of my skills.
OL,17,FWhat a great fight, what a great
OL,18,Fbattle. But, I'm number one again."
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@AOUzD@cO]
