PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778418667
OL,3,CDaniel Dubois defeats Fabio Wardley to
OL,4,Cbecome WBO heavyweight champion
OL,6,FDubois added, "I want to grow from
OL,7,Fthis fight, improve and come back even
OL,8,Fbetter and go on a reign as champion
OL,9,Fagain."
OL,11,FThe world champion halted Wardley's
OL,12,Ffairytale run from white-collar boxer
OL,13,Fto WBO title holder, and quietened
OL,14,Fcritics who have questioned his spirit.
OL,16,FHe faced accusations of "quitting"
OL,17,Fwhen he lost to Joe Joyce in 2020 and
OL,18,Fthis week Dubois walked out of two
OL,19,Finterviews as he looked to get back
OL,20,Finto the win column after losing his
OL,21,FIBF title 11 months ago.
