OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778418667
OL,3,CDaniel Dubois defeats Fabio Wardley to
OL,4,Cbecome WBO heavyweight champion
OL,6,FA second defeat to heavyweight kingpin
OL,7,FOleksandr Usyk at Wembley Stadium was
OL,8,Ffollowed by footage emerging of Dubois
OL,9,Fhosting a party at his house just
OL,10,Fhours before being taken out in the
OL,11,Ffifth round.
OL,13,FHis trainer Don Charles, who Dubois
OL,14,Ffired and rehired since then, promised
OL,15,Fthere would be no repeat of a pre-
OL,16,Ffight "gathering" after his charge was
OL,17,Fgranted an immediate shot at winning
OL,18,Fanother world title
